<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Welcome to flight-booker, <%= @passenger.name %></h1>
    <p>
      You have successfully booked a seat on flight #<%= @passenger.booking.flight_id %>,
      under the name: <%= @passenger.name %>.<br><br>
      Departure: <%= @flight.start_airport.code %> <br>
      Arrival: <%= @flight.finish_airport.code %><br>
      on: <%= @flight.start_date_formatted %> at: <%= @flight.start_time.strftime("%H:%M") %><br>
      Flight duration: <%= Time.at(@flight.flight_duration.to_i).utc.strftime("%H:%M:%S") %>
    </p>
    <p>
      To login to the site, just follow this link: <%= @url %>.
    </p>
    <p>Thanks for booking and have a great day!</p>
  </body>
</html>